OL,3,CDisruption as busy stretch of M4
OL,4,Cclosed for whole weekend
OL,6,FA busy stretch of the M4 has been shut
OL,7,Ffor the entire weekend to allow
OL,8,Fconstruction work on a new bridge.
OL,10,FThe motorway has been closed in both
OL,11,Fdirections between junctions 18 (Bath)
OL,12,Fand 19 (M32) since October 24 8:45pm,
OL,13,Fand it is hoped it will reopen at 6am
OL,14,Fon Monday October 27.
OL,16,FThe closure is because National
OL,17,FHighways will be installing eight
OL,18,Flarge steel beams for the new A432
OL,19,FBadminton Road Bridge - seven months
OL,20,Fafter the original structure was
OL,21,Fdemolished.
