OL,6,FIt is estimated up to 4,000 vehicles
OL,7,Fuse this stretch of the M4 everyday.
OL,8,FSignificant disruption is expected to
OL,9,Fcontinue throughout the weekend until
OL,10,Fit reopens.
OL,12,FMotorists are being urged to avoid the
OL,13,Farea or travel at alternative times if
OL,14,Fpossible, with diversions in place
OL,15,Fthroughout the weekend.
